    "description": "Grow your career with Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Reservation Manager for our Surat team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited:\nYum! Brands India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited!",
